courses.courseTitle: Getting Started with Programming, OO & Java Basics for Non-Developers
courses.courseSubtitle: Kickstart Your Software Development Skills with this Gentle Introduction to Coding, Object Oriented Development and Java
courses.catalogSummary: Getting Started with Programming, OO and Java Basics for Non-Developers is a fast-paced, five day course designed to provide you with a first look at how to code in Java to a very basic level. You'll gain light hands-on programming experience, while you begin your journey to develop a programmer's mindset.

courses.courseSubtitle: Master Core Java Programming Concepts and Best Practices
courses.catalogSummary: This comprehensive workshop provides developers with a deep dive into core Java programming concepts, covering object-oriented principles, collections, exception handling, and more.

courses.courseTitle: Fast Track to Core Java Programming for OO Experienced Developers
courses.courseSubtitle: Accelerated Java Training for Developers with Object-Oriented Experience
courses.catalogSummary: An accelerated course designed for developers who already understand object-oriented concepts and want to quickly become proficient in Java programming.

courses.courseTitle: Basic Java Programming for Developers New to OO (C, COBOL, etc.)
courses.courseSubtitle: Transition from Procedural to Object-Oriented Programming with Java
courses.catalogSummary: Learn Java programming from a procedural developer's perspective, with special emphasis on transitioning to object-oriented thinking and design patterns.

courses.courseTitle: Migrating to Java 17 | Java 17 New Features & Skills
courses.courseSubtitle: Master the Latest Features and Improvements in Java 17
courses.catalogSummary: Explore and learn to implement the new features and improvements introduced in Java 17, including sealed classes, pattern matching, and other enhancements.

courses.courseTitle: Migrating Java 17 to Java 21 | Java 21 New Features and Skills
courses.courseSubtitle: Stay Current with Java's Latest Innovations
courses.catalogSummary: Update your Java skills to version 21, covering virtual threads, structured concurrency, and other cutting-edge features introduced since Java 17.

courses.courseTitle: Migrating Java 8 to Java 17 | Java 17 New Features and Skills
courses.courseSubtitle: Comprehensive Update from Java 8 to Modern Java
courses.catalogSummary: Bridge the gap between Java 8 and Java 17, covering all major features and improvements introduced across multiple Java versions.

courses.courseTitle: Intermediate Java Programming | Next-Level Java Skills
courses.courseSubtitle: Advanced Concepts for Professional Java Developers
courses.catalogSummary: Take your Java skills to the next level with advanced topics including concurrency, functional programming, and modern Java APIs.

courses.courseTitle: Core Spring Quick Start | Spring Essentials, Spring Boot, AOP, Persistence & More
courses.courseSubtitle: Comprehensive Introduction to the Spring Framework Ecosystem
courses.catalogSummary: Get up to speed with Spring Framework, covering core concepts, Spring Boot, AOP, data access, and best practices for building modern Java applications.

courses.courseSubtitle: Intensive Spring Framework Training for Professional Developers
courses.catalogSummary: An intensive boot camp covering advanced Spring Framework topics, microservices architecture, and cloud-native application development.

courses.courseSubtitle: Building Reactive Applications with Spring WebFlux
courses.catalogSummary: Learn to build reactive applications using Spring WebFlux, covering reactive streams, functional programming, and non-blocking architectures.

courses.courseTitle: Test Driven Development (TDD) and Unit Testing Essentials
courses.courseSubtitle: Best Practices for Quality Software Development
courses.catalogSummary: Master test-driven development practices and unit testing techniques using JUnit and related testing frameworks.

courses.courseSubtitle: Fundamentals of Automated Testing in Modern Software Development
courses.catalogSummary: Learn the fundamentals of test automation, including tool selection, framework design, and best practices for sustainable test automation.

courses.courseTitle: Introduction to HTML5 / CSS3 and Responsive Design
courses.courseSubtitle: Modern Web Development Fundamentals
courses.catalogSummary: Get started with modern web development using HTML5, CSS3, and responsive design principles for creating mobile-friendly websites.

courses.courseSubtitle: Essential JavaScript Skills for Modern Web Development
courses.catalogSummary: Learn core JavaScript programming concepts, DOM manipulation, and modern JavaScript features for building interactive web applications.

courses.courseTitle: Advanced JavaScript and Modern Web Development
courses.courseSubtitle: Master Modern JavaScript Features and Web APIs
courses.catalogSummary: Deep dive into advanced JavaScript topics, modern web APIs, and contemporary development practices for building sophisticated web applications.

courses.courseSubtitle: Building Modern User Interfaces with React
courses.catalogSummary: Learn to build modern user interfaces using React.js, covering components, state management, hooks, and best practices.

courses.courseSubtitle: Server-Side JavaScript Development with Node.js
courses.catalogSummary: Master Node.js for building scalable server-side applications, covering Express.js, APIs, databases, and deployment strategies.

courses.courseSubtitle: End-to-End Web Development with JavaScript
courses.catalogSummary: Comprehensive training in full-stack JavaScript development, covering both front-end and back-end technologies, including React, Node.js, and databases.

courses.courseSubtitle: Type-Safe JavaScript Development
courses.catalogSummary: Learn TypeScript for building scalable JavaScript applications with static typing, object-oriented features, and modern development tools.
